01:45:11,908 --> 01:45:14,968
These boys that you have around you. What about them?
那些在你身边黑小子们。他们怎么了？

911
01:45:14,968 --> 01:45:17,738
The violence for one...
第一个：使用暴力。。。

912
01:45:18,848 --> 01:45:20,868
Some of it may be necessary, but...
其中一些可能必要，但是。。。【注意到：两个小孩】

913
01:45:21,386 --> 01:45:22,938
Hey！
嘿！

914
01:45:23,978 --> 01:45:25,968
Is that for me?
那动作是做给我看的吗？

915
01:45:26,748 --> 01:45:29,918
No, Guru. It's for the white men.
不，导师。是给白人的。

916
01:45:31,928 --> 01:45:35,988
So, you're doing that because of the colour of their skin?
所以你们这么做，只因为他们皮肤的颜色吗？

917
01:45:36,028 --> 01:45:37,958
Yes, Guru.
是的，导师。

918
01:45:40,968 --> 01:45:43,768
That is what they do to us.
那就是他们这样对待我们的。

919
01:45:44,768 --> 01:45:46,758
But we must do better.
但我们必须做得比他们更好。

920
01:45:46,968 --> 01:45:49,908
Understand? Yes, Guru.
明白了吗？是的，导师。

921
01:45:50,938 --> 01:45:53,878
Come, come on.
来, 快点！

922
01:45:54,908 --> 01:45:57,778
These are my grandsons...
这些是我的孙子...【领袖身教：种族接纳、和解】

923
01:45:57,818 --> 01:46:01,878
They want to meet you.
他们想见见你们。【温妮转身离去。】

924
01:46:04,888 --> 01:46:06,018
Is Bobby there?
波比在吗？

925
01:46:06,728 --> 01:46:08,888
No, no. I want to do this.
不，不。我想做这些事。【洗碗.....】

926
01:46:08,928 --> 01:46:11,828
These are also dirty.
这些很脏。

927
01:46:11,928 --> 01:46:19,798
[Tape Recoding...] It's in the agreement she can stay over night. Anytime that you want.
[录音中...]同意她可以留宿。任何时候都行。

928
01:46:19,838 --> 01:46:23,798
That's not what she wants. This is still a prison.
这不是她想要的。这依然是一个监狱。【软禁！】

929
01:46:24,838 --> 01:46:27,008
She can't pretend that I'm a free man.
她不能假装我是个自由人。

930
01:46:27,778 --> 01:46:28,938
Okay.
好吧。

931
01:46:29,948 --> 01:46:32,938
But she's still your wife.
但她仍然是你妻子呀。

932
01:46:32,948 --> 01:46:35,918
Well, I was married in 1958,
哎，我结婚是1958年。

933
01:46:36,858 --> 01:46:43,988
arrested in 62, didn't touch her again until 84.
被捕在62年，再没接触她直到84年。【22年】

934
01:46:44,758 --> 01:46:46,818
Well,She is still my wife.
嗯，她仍然是我的妻子。

935
01:46:46,868 --> 01:46:50,888
I've seen you with her when you looked at her photograph.
我看你在看她照片中时，你们在一起。

936
01:46:52,008 --> 01:46:54,908
You love her.
你爱她。

937
01:46:55,008 --> 01:47:01,808
That's the vey trouble, my friend, I never stopped loving her.
那正是麻烦所在，我的朋友，我从来没有停止过爱她。

938
01:47:01,978 --> 01:47:08,848
But I love what she was. [Recording...]
但我爱是过去的她。【全程录音...分歧和绯闻的来源.】

939
01:47:11,788 --> 01:47:15,788
The first step to regain the confidence of the markets is your release
恢复市场信心的第一步是您的获释。

940
01:47:15,886 --> 01:47:18,606
and then of course the release of your colleagues.
而后当然是，释放你的同事们。

941
01:47:18,778 --> 01:47:21,888
We've briefed the president. He's a pragmatist, he heard us.
我们已经给总统做了简报。他是实用主义者，他听从了我们。

942
01:47:22,028 --> 01:47:25,088
The Government agrees to lift the ban on the ANC,
政府会同意解除对ANC【非国大】的禁令。

943
01:47:25,828 --> 01:47:29,058
and repeal the race laws. You undertake to renounce violence.
并且废除种族歧视的法律。你要承诺宣布放弃暴力。

944
01:47:31,606 --> 01:47:34,606
No！ But you said...
不！但你说过...

945
01:47:34,786 --> 01:47:36,838
I said nothing.
我什么也没说过。

946
01:47:37,078 --> 01:47:39,486
I listened.
我只倾听。

947
01:47:39,606 --> 01:47:42,848
But you will withdraw your demand for majority rule.
但你会撤消: 你多数人统治的要求。

948
01:47:43,786 --> 01:47:45,918
No.
没有。

949
01:47:47,048 --> 01:47:49,918
Then, what are you giving us in exchange for what we give you?
那么，你打算拿什么来交换我们给予你的一切？

950
01:47:50,018 --> 01:47:53,606
Nothing.
什么都没有。【政治家的本色：谋略！】

951
01:47:53,888 --> 01:47:56,264
These meetings have been a complete waste of our time.
这些会议简直是浪费我们的时间。

952
01:47:56,375 --> 01:47:59,098
Well, I wouldn't say that I wasted my time.
嗯，我不愿说这浪费了我的时间。【四两拔千斤......】

953
01:48:01,068 --> 01:48:10,486
The President has made up his mind. Can't be stopped now.
总统已经作出的决定，不能停止了。

954
01:48:14,178 --> 01:48:18,197
The President is, a member of the Reformer, De Klerk.
总统现为改革家，德克勒克(1936.3.18:78岁）
(1989-1997南非副总统、总统，1993年与曼氏分享诺贝尔和平奖)

955
01:48:18,248 --> 01:48:20,048
very Calvinist.
十足的加尔文教徒。

956
01:48:20,048 --> 01:48:24,686
He believes God calls him to do a special task in a special time.
他坚信上帝召唤他在特殊的时刻完成一项特殊的使命。

957
01:48:27,088 --> 01:48:35,018
After the inauguration service, he wept and said that God was calling him
在总统入职仪式后他流泪说：上帝一直在召唤他

958
01:48:35,168 --> 01:48:37,228
to save the people of South Africa.
来去拯救南非人民。

959
01:48:44,797 --> 01:48:46,178
President De Klerk，
德克勒克总统，【自传记录: 时间1989年12月13日,总统府】

960
01:48:47,178 --> 01:48:49,168
[Boer?]They are here.
【布尔语？】他们在这里。

961
01:48:50,318 --> 01:48:51,686
Please, this way.
这边，请。

962
01:48:51,806 --> 01:48:56,048
Oh, shoe lace!Yeah..
哦，鞋带！好...【戏剧性细节：白人为黑人打鞋带...】

963
01:48:58,028 --> 01:49:09,188
Well, thank you. Well, this is it.
啊，谢谢你。 嗯，就是这儿了。

964
01:49:27,318 --> 01:49:31,118
Mr. Mandela！ Mr. President.
曼德拉先生！总统先生！【相逢一笑泯恩仇......】

965
01:49:31,228 --> 01:49:35,158
May I congratulate you on your election. Thank you.
能让我恭喜你的选举吗？                   谢谢。
【德克勒克1989.9.20大选获胜成为总统,此前为副总统】

966
01:49:36,168 --> 01:49:43,686
You have been called for a very special task...in a very special time.
你被召唤来完成非常特别的使命....在非常特别的时刻。

967
01:49:43,806 --> 01:49:45,686
So I believe.
我就信了。【不管你信不信！】

968
01:49:47,068 --> 01:49:48,228
[Boer]Please sit down.
【布尔语】请坐!
布尔语:南非白人(荷兰人)的语言,又称Afrikaans阿非利卡语/斐语】

969
01:49:52,308 --> 01:49:54,208
You first. Yeah.
您先请。好的。

970
01:50:03,088 --> 01:50:08,118
Mr. Mandela, I've taken the decision to release you
曼德拉先生。我已经做出决定：释放你

971
01:50:09,058 --> 01:50:12,088
unconditionally.
无条件地。

972
01:50:12,268 --> 01:50:16,686
A car will be ready by tomorrow morning to take you to the airport.
明天一大早，有车送你去机场。

973
01:50:17,298 --> 01:50:20,353
A plane will be waiting to fly directly to Johannesburg
会有专机等你，直飞约翰内斯堡

974
01:50:20,806 --> 01:50:23,098
where an Official Release Ceremony will take place.
在那里将举行“官方释放仪式”。

975
01:50:26,178 --> 01:50:28,108
Mr. De Klerk,
德克勒克先生

976
01:50:28,248 --> 01:50:31,686
your people have taken away half of my life
你方人员已剥夺了我大半辈子的生命。

977
01:50:32,218 --> 01:50:37,118
and returned me an old man to a home that's been long abandoned
而把我一个古稀老头扔回给一个被长久遗弃的家庭

978
01:50:38,058 --> 01:50:41,078
and a family that have grown up without me.
并且一家人成长，却从没有我存在。

979
01:50:43,058 --> 01:50:48,797
I don't want you at my side at that moment.
在那一个时刻，我不希望你们在我身边。

980
01:50:49,068 --> 01:50:53,797
I don't want to be told that you have given me my freedom.
我不希望你们通知：你们已经归还了我的自由。

981
01:50:54,208 --> 01:51:00,797
Just open the gate and let me go.
就打开大门，让我走吧。

982
01:51:02,278 --> 01:51:06,797
【英文字幕】1990年2月11日【南非的夏天】

983
01:51:10,318 --> 01:51:15,058
[欢声笑语]

984
01:51:20,268 --> 01:51:22,168
[科萨语...]

985
01:51:24,238 --> 01:51:26,298
[津泽：科萨语密谈...]

986
01:51:31,318 --> 01:51:34,178
Hello...Hello...
你好...你好...

987
01:51:34,188 --> 01:51:37,158
How are you? Hi. I'm good.
你好吗？海。我很好。

988
01:51:40,128 --> 01:51:44,786
I could not do it without you.
没有你，哪有我？【真话：内外联手！】

989
01:51:45,298 --> 01:51:51,786
Do you want me to hold your hand and kiss in the sun？
你要我牵着你的手,在阳光下亲吻？

990
01:52:17,195 --> 01:52:20,186
[奔驰是温妮的...]

991
01:53:45,748 --> 01:54:06,397
【英文字幕】约翰内斯堡市奥兰多镇
【1990年2月13日回到8115号故居】

992
01:54:19,848 --> 01:54:25,678
[Poster:VIVA]Somebody wants me!
【标语：万岁!欢迎同志！】有人需要我！

993
01:54:51,286 --> 01:54:54,778
Don't be fooled by all that cheering, Madiba.
不要被所有这些欢呼声中愚弄，马迪巴【曼德拉】。

994
01:54:55,848 --> 01:54:57,678
There's anger out there?
那里还有愤怒？

995
01:54:57,818 --> 01:54:59,788
I know that.
我懂的。

996
01:55:07,768 --> 01:55:19,286
Winnie. Winnie...
温妮！温妮！【对他没有兴趣...】

997
01:55:19,838 --> 01:55:22,678
It's just been too long time.
这一切太长时间了。

998
01:55:29,718 --> 01:55:31,848
It's better that way.
那样也最好。

999
01:55:38,858 --> 01:55:41,698
I'm so tired.
我太累了。

1000
01:55:44,898 --> 01:55:53,698
I just want to sleep.
我只想睡个觉。  【没有接受信号。。。】

1001
01:55:55,397 --> 01:56:14,286
[焚烧车辆、示威人群]
Singing:Fight the power...
【歌唱：与权力战斗...】

1002
01:56:14,868 --> 01:56:18,397
【英文字幕：CODESA1992年5月15日】Convention for a Democratic South Africa CODESA民主南非大会（南非制宪会议，或译南非政协）
The government accepts that change must come.
政府接受必须改变。

1003
01:56:18,798 --> 01:56:21,668
But I say to you again,
但我要再次告诉你，

1004
01:56:21,738 --> 01:56:24,708
we must find a way to share power.
我们必须找到分享权力的方法。

1005
01:56:26,778 --> 01:56:31,718
We must find a way to protect the rights of the minorities
我们必须找到保护少数人权力的方法。

1006
01:56:35,848 --> 01:56:39,648
Suddenly the illusion of white power is beginning to crumble.
突然，白人政权的幻觉开始崩溃。

1007
01:56:39,758 --> 01:56:44,848
For the first time since apartheid began, the government started talking about the need for reform.
自从种族隔离制度以来，第一次政府开始谈论改革的需求。

1008
01:56:45,658 --> 01:56:50,828
Among ordinary white people, feelings now range from bewilderment, anger to fear.
白人平民，人人自危，充满迷惘，愤怒和恐惧。

1009
01:56:50,838 --> 01:57:00,838
[Arguing people]
[争论的人群]

1010
01:57:04,648 --> 01:57:08,748
Tell me just how do we accept power sharing with the whites?
告诉我吧我们如何分享与白人分享政权？

1011
01:57:08,788 --> 01:57:10,878
So what do we do? We fight?
那么，我们该怎么办？我们开战吗？

1012
01:57:10,918 --> 01:57:14,688
We start a war? We have a war. Do you think this isn't a war?
我们开战？我们已有场战争。你认为这是不是一战争吗？

1013
01:57:14,688 --> 01:57:16,628
We have no war. What we need now is big teeth.
我们现在没有战争。我们需要是强大的效率。

1014
01:57:16,658 --> 01:57:19,628
Congress, our people will never accept sharing power with the whites.
ANC会员们，我们的人民永远不会接受与白人分享权力。

1015
01:57:19,758 --> 01:57:22,558
They will never accept this. De Klerk should declare...
他们不会接受这点。           德克勒克应该宣布。。。

1016
01:57:22,768 --> 01:57:25,064
Why should De Klerk declare what he's already won?
为什么德克勒克应该宣布他已经赢得什么?

1017
01:57:25,294 --> 01:57:28,284
He's right! He's right! We must let them share the power.
他是对的。他是对的。我们应该让他们分享权力。

1018
01:57:28,858 --> 01:57:33,728
A little power for a little while until the fear has passed.
逐步分享权力，一点点来直到起恐惧消除。

1019
01:57:33,758 --> 01:57:35,728
Madiba, I don't think our people will accept that.
阿迪巴，我认为人民不会接受这个办法。

1020
01:57:35,758 --> 01:57:38,698
Then we must make them accept. We are their leaders.
我们必须让人民接受。我们是他们的领导。

1021
01:57:38,868 --> 01:57:39,858
That is our job.
那是我们的工作。

1022
01:57:55,878 --> 01:57:59,818
We come here to speak in just one tone.
我们到此只用一个声音说话。

1023
01:57:59,818 --> 01:58:03,718
The games of talking are over.
谈判的游戏现在结束。【标语：要枪...】

1024
01:58:09,728 --> 01:58:10,818
Go and get her.
去找她来。

1025
01:58:12,828 --> 01:58:15,798
I hear the voice of the people.
我听见人民的呼声，

1026
01:58:16,838 --> 01:58:20,708
And that voice says, we will fight!
人民呼吁：我们要战斗！

1027
01:58:28,718 --> 01:58:30,838
【口号：VIVA万岁！】曼德拉先生一直在等待。

1028
01:58:31,688 --> 01:58:37,748
[人群欢呼雀跃]

1029
01:58:42,798 --> 01:58:43,888
What?
怎么了？

1030
01:58:44,828 --> 01:58:47,698
Are you ashamed to greet me in front of our people?
你耻于在我们的人民面前问候我吗？

1031
01:58:47,698 --> 01:58:51,868
When you speak in public, you must represent the policies of the ANC.
当你在公共场合讲话，你必须代表ANC非国大的各项政策。

1032
01:58:51,908 --> 01:58:53,898
What does that mean? we're negotiating?
什么意思? 我们在协商中？

1033
01:58:53,938 --> 01:58:58,808
We are not fighting a war. But the people have chosen to fight.
我们不要打仗，但是，人民选择去战斗。

1034
01:58:59,748 --> 01:59:01,808
Do you want me to betray our people?
你要我出卖我们的人民吗？

1035
01:59:02,818 --> 01:59:03,938
Do I betray our people?
我出卖了我们的人民了？

1036
01:59:04,688 --> 01:59:05,848
You have been away a long time...
你离开了很久......

1037
01:59:05,888 --> 01:59:09,718
What does that mean "I've been away?" Does that mean now you can terrorize people?
“我离开了很久......”是什么含义？这就意味着你可以恐吓人民吗？

1038
01:59:11,758 --> 01:59:15,718
The burning, the necklessness, that has to stop,Winnie!
焚烧，鲁莽, 都必须停止，温妮!

1039
01:59:15,758 --> 01:59:17,818
Do you realize there's a war out there?
你意识到外面有场战争吗？

1040
01:59:18,728 --> 01:59:21,447
The people are angry. We are all angry.
人民感到愤怒。我们都很生气。

1041
01:59:21,456 --> 01:59:24,738
I am angry! You are angry!
我很生气。你很生气！

1042
01:59:24,868 --> 01:59:26,838
But you must show loyalty.
但是，你必须表现出忠诚。

1043
01:59:28,938 --> 01:59:41,938
Loyalty, Winnie Mandela.
忠诚，温妮・曼德拉。【同志：你还是“我的”人......】

1044
01:59:44,688 --> 01:59:52,748
Loyalty！
忠贞！【Loyalty:忠诚于党、忠贞于爱情：双关！】

1045
01:59:53,536 --> 01:59:59,858
I've decided that it would be better if I lived in my own home.
我已经决定：最好我住在自己的家里。

1046
01:59:59,868 --> 02:00:01,898
better for the party.
对党更好。

1047
02:00:04,878 --> 02:00:06,738
better for us.
对我们更好。

1048
02:00:10,888 --> 02:00:12,848
better for the party.
对党更好。

1049
02:00:12,888 --> 02:00:17,788
You have your own home in Debokrof,
你有自己迪波克鲁夫的家。

1050
02:00:18,958 --> 02:00:20,948
You have your own company there.
那里你有自己的伴侣。

1051
02:00:22,858 --> 02:00:25,758
Am I to blame because I don't want to be alone?
因为我不想独自一个人生活，就就责怪我？

1052
02:00:27,738 --> 02:00:33,868
You know so much of my life? I've been alone.
你对我的生活完全了解，我一直都独自一人生活。

1053
02:00:35,878 --> 02:00:59,447
We've both been alone too much, Winnie.
我们俩都“独自”得太久了，温妮.【个性、道路、观念不同：先分居】

1054
02:01:00,898 --> 02:01:03,668
Why Walter? Tell me why?
为什么，沃尔特？告诉我为什么？

1055
02:01:04,738 --> 02:01:06,708
Why do you show me this?
你为什么要给我看这个？

1056
02:01:06,738 --> 02:01:08,898
Do you think I don't know? This has gone too far.
你以为我不知道吗？这已经太过分了。

1057
02:01:09,938 --> 02:01:13,738
If she was discrete about this...I have accepted the situation!
如果她分开这一切...我已经接受了现况。

1058
02:01:14,848 --> 02:01:18,948
What business is it of anyone else? She's humiliating you in public, Madiba.
